":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽已於4月29日舉行<br />\n冠軍由李佳芯奪得<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃決賽 5月27日凌晨0時<br />\n新垣結衣(日本)<br />\nvs<br />\nIU(韓國)<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abc1fc15b9bd8bb320fa41e5886e032b7ad7274","tid":661541,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"雖然已經係例行公事,但都玩埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2479c65a145e83941b2af7f5d92862a2395c60","tid":661541,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b9165a535abeee2d4584c4cca306c1ee530f93","tid":661541,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d96025a7fff8ce07a99b64fd82392a628f0884","tid":661541,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite